events.description:
Mount Faber Line (Round Trip) refers to one round trip on Mount Faber Line for a day only.
Ticket purchased has a validity period of 90 days upon date of purchase. 
Cable Car operating hours: 8.45am - 10pm (Last boarding 9.30pm).
Child is defined as 4 to 12 years old (before 13th birthday). Free admission for children below 4 years old.
Flammable materials like liquids, gases, ionised and non-ionised lithium batteries; and devices that contain flammable materials such as Motorized Personal Mobility devices and electronic scooters and helium balloons are prohibited onboard the Singapore Cable Car.

events.title: Wings of Time Fireworks Symphony
events.description:
The magical adventure begins with Shahbaz, a prehistoric bird. Together with his friends, Rachel and Felix, they travel across beautiful landscapes and the mysteries of time, featuring artistic interpretations of the Industrial Revolution, the Silk Road era, Mayan Pyramids, Underwater World and African Savanna. As Shahbaz’s friends discover more about themselves, will they find the courage to be who they really are? Will Shahbaz find his way home and will the trio find true friendship at the end of the journey?
 

Timeslot booking is mandatory. Please make timeslot booking at the following URL:

For Wings of Time Open Dated tickets, please proceed tohttps://viewbookings.mountfaberleisure.com/merchant/4398 and enter your ticketconfirmation code to choose from an available Date & Time slot before heading to theattraction.
